### Get Tokens for All Roles
### IntelliJ/VS Code REST Client HTTP file
### Run these first to populate @token_* variables for use in other .http files
###
### Set your environment in the IDE before running:
###   KEYCLOAK_URL = https://dev.aran.me
###   REALM        = ciyex
###   CLIENT_ID    = ciyex-app
###   BASE_URL     = https://api-dev.ciyex.org

### ── ADMIN (michael.chen) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name admin_token
POST {{KEYCLOAK_URL}}/realms/{{REALM}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{CLIENT_ID}}&username=michael.chen@example.com&password={{TEST_USER_PASSWORD}}

> {%
  client.global.set("token_admin", response.body.access_token);
  client.log("ADMIN token stored: " + response.body.access_token.substring(0,40) + "...");
%}

###

